text_Diorite: Lovely spotted, freckled stones with dark spots. I'll remember this because DIOR model has lovely freckles.
text_Pegmatite: Beautiful quartz and colorful sharp angles, lots of contrasting green and earth tones.  I'll remember this because Peg on Married with Children wore bright chunky jewelry.
Again the beautiful quartz like rock with contrasting green or brown shards.  This the Peg from married with children wearing jewelry.
text_Andesite: Andesite is like Diorite but instead of the spots being dark, the contrasting spots are white.  I'll remember this because neighbor Andy is a white supremacist.

text_Basalt: Basalt is a flinty looking stone, looks like a prehistoric weapon. I'll remember this Basalt because Assad Bashir uses weapons.
text_Pumice: Porous dry looking stone just like the pumice stone used on rough skin or stains. I'll remember this one.
